parameters:
No matter what... I have to defend this place! Can
you still heal?

I'm sorry, but I can't take it anymore... But... I
have to save Amy-chan!
Nooo... I'm scared... I'm so scared!

You humans... you dare to challenge the
\c[10]demon\c[0]... little did you know that your
barrier has already been broken...

No matter how much you magic girls think you're
our threat... there's no way you can withstand an
attack from this many of us...

You're gravely mistaken if you think it will end
like this...!

\c[10]Demon\c[0], do you still dare to oppose us?
It seems you have no idea what will happen to your
young comrades, huh?

(Melarsa, what's the point of provoking them! Buy
us some time, even just a little!)

(I know... but even if we buy some time... do you
really think that if we pray, the goddess Althea
will come to our rescue?)

Baretta never shows up when we need her... That
useless...!
Help meee... It hurts so baaad...!

Ah! Please...! Oh merciful god, please grant me
power! Grant me the power to save that girl!

Damn it...! If only my body... could move a little
more...!

\c[10]Demon\c[0], hmph, it's time... If you won't
retreat... then you should witness what will
happen to these magical girls right before your
eyes...
Ugh... Ugh... Th-thank you... ver...y... much...
It seems like there's no problem... I'm glad.

More importantly, I don't really understand why I
fell from the sky...

For now... it seems like we have to defeat the
monster in front of us first.

\c[10]Demon\c[0] I can't believe... you had such
a... secret weapon... tsk... wiping out the other
units with a single blow...

A-amazing... Who are you...? Could it be a
reincarnator...?
The demon leader is still here! Please be careful!

My body has been getting soft lately. It's perfect
timing, I'll give you a good match. Come at me!

\c[10]Demon\c[0], if you're so cocky, then I'll
personally slaughter you...!

\c[10]Demon\c[0], you idiot... Just who... the
hell... are... you...
What is it? It's nothing special...

Sorry to keep you waiting~! It's the grand
entrance of Baretta-sama!!! ...Huh?

It's over, Baretta. It's a shame you didn't have a
chance to shine.

No way! I was supposed to show off all my good
points!
